/// RLS: the audiology-read role must map to the Entra group sg-healthent-audiology-read
/// (operating rules section 24). Filter to the user's clinic(s); replace the table path with
/// your clinic-membership mapping when one exists. No patient-level PII is ever exposed in a visual.
role 'audiology-read'
	modelPermission: read

	tablePermission dim_clinic = "TRUE()"
